OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FGerry Adams has told the High Court
OL,7,Fthat he had "no involvement
OL,8,Fwhatsoever" in Provisional IRA
OL,9,Fbombings in England and that he was
OL,10,Fnever a part of the organisation.
OL,12,FThe former Sinn Fein president entered
OL,13,Fthe witness box on Tuesday in defence
OL,14,Fof a legal claim against him brought
OL,15,Fby three victims of bombings in
OL,16,FEngland in the 1970s and 1990s.
OL,26,@oD@MOUpD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FJohn Clark, a victim of the 1973 Old
OL,7,FBailey bombing in London; Jonathan
OL,8,FGanesh, a 1996 London Docklands
OL,9,Fbombing victim; and Barry Laycock, a
OL,10,Fvictim of the 1996 Arndale shopping
OL,11,Fcentre bombing in Manchester, all
OL,12,Fallege that Mr Adams was a leading
OL,13,Fmember of the Provisional IRA on those
OL,14,Fdates, including of its Army Council,
OL,15,Fand are seeking #1 in damages.
OL,17,FMr Adams is defending the claim,
OL,18,Fsaying in a witness statement that
OL,19,Fmembership of Sinn Fein "does not
OL,20,Fequate to membership of the IRA".
OL,26,@{D@YOU|D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FHe also told the court that while he
OL,7,Fdid not distance himself from the
OL,8,FProvisional IRA, he was glad the
OL,9,Forganisation had "left the stage" and
OL,10,Fthat there were "dastardly things that
OL,11,Fwere done that should never have been
OL,12,Fdone".
OL,14,FWearing a dark suit and tie, a
OL,15,Fshamrock and a badge of the
OL,16,FPalestinian flag, Mr Adams began his
OL,17,Fevidence by wishing the judge, Mr
OL,18,FJustice Swift, "a very happy St
OL,19,FPatrick's Day".
OL,26,@qD@ROUqD@aO]rD@QOUtD@EO]zD@POU{D@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FIn his 20-page witness statement, Mr
OL,7,FAdams said he "was not involved in any
OL,8,Fway in the planning, preparation or
OL,10,Fconduct of" any of the bombings, and
OL,11,F"have never been a senior, let alone
OL,12,Fmost senior figure, in the IRA".
OL,14,FHe continued: "I had no involvement in
OL,15,For advance knowledge of the Old Bailey
OL,16,Fbombing (1973), the Canary Wharf
OL,17,Fbombing (1996) or the Manchester
OL,18,Fbombing (1996).
OL,26,@oD@OOUrD@KO]sD@AOUtD@_O]vD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,F"I have never been charged, prosecuted
OL,7,For convicted of any offence in
OL,8,Fconnection with any of the bombing
OL,9,Fincidents in which the claimants were
OL,10,Finjured."
OL,12,FHe also said: "I was never a member of
OL,13,Fthe IRA or its Army Council, and I
OL,14,Fnever held any role or rank within the
OL,15,FIRA.
OL,17,F"I repeat that I had no involvement
OL,18,Fwhatsoever in the authorisation,
OL,19,Fplanning or conduct of the bombings in
OL,20,Fwhich the claimants were sadly
OL,21,Finjured."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]tD@OOUyD@AOU}D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FMr Adams also said that opponents of
OL,7,FSinn Fein, of which he was president
OL,8,Ffrom 1983 to 2018, "have repeatedly
OL,9,Fsought to conflate" the party with the
OL,10,FProvisional IRA.
OL,12,F"As I have always stated, Sinn Fein
OL,13,Fand the IRA are separate
OL,14,Forganisations," Mr Adams said.
OL,16,FHe continued: "I have no knowledge,
OL,17,Fbeyond what has been widely reported
OL,18,Fin the public domain, as to the
OL,19,Fstructure or decision-making processes
OL,20,Fof the IRA."
OL,26,@pD@TOUqD@SO]tD@AOUvD@OO]xD@OOU|D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FMr Adams told the court that he was
OL,7,F"very conscious" that the three bomb
OL,8,Fvictims had "suffered significantly",
OL,9,Fand that his statement should not be
OL,10,Ftaken "as criticism of the claimants,
OL,11,For as any attempt to deny or diminish
OL,12,Ftheir awful experiences".
OL,14,FDuring cross-examination by barrister
OL,15,FSir Max Hill KC, Mr Adams agreed that
OL,16,F1,178 deaths were caused by the
OL,17,FProvisional IRA, the business of which
OL,18,Fwas "to resist armed British
OL,19,Foccupation and aggression in the part
OL,20,Fof Ireland that I lived in".
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@PO]pD@MOUpD@dO]rD@GOUtD@XO]zD@
OL,26,AEOU|D@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FHe had earlier said that the ignorance
OL,7,Fof Irish history among British people
OL,8,Fis "shocking".
OL,10,FSir Max later asked Mr Adams: "It's
OL,11,Fyour business to defend many actions
OL,12,Fof the IRA, is that an accurate
OL,13,Fstatement?"
OL,15,FMr Adams replied: "I do not defend all
OL,16,Fthe IRA actions but my position is
OL,17,Fbased on the broad principle that
OL,18,Fpeople have the right to resist
OL,19,Foccupation."
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@MO]rD@_OUuD@KO]wD@SOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FSir Max continued: "You have, over a
OL,7,Flong period of time, chosen to stand
OL,8,Fby the IRA."
OL,10,FMr Adams replied: "I do not stand by
OL,11,Feverything that they did but these
OL,12,Fwere my neighbours."
OL,14,FHe continued: "I'm glad that the IRA
OL,15,Fhas left the stage, I'm glad that no
OL,16,Fone else is being killed."
OL,26,@nD@TOUpD@LO]rD@SOUtD@TO]vD@OOUxD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FHe added: "I am glad that there is a
OL,7,Fpeace process but I do not distance
OL,8,Fmyself from the IRA while being very,
OL,9,Fvery clear that there were dastardly
OL,10,Fthings that were done that should
OL,11,Fnever have been done."
OL,13,FAnne Studd KC, for the three bomb
OL,14,Fvictims, previously told the trial
OL,15,Fthat Mr Adams was "directly
OL,16,Fresponsible for and complicit in those
OL,17,Fdecisions made by that organisation to
OL,18,Fdetonate bombs on the British mainland
OL,19,Fin 1973 and 1996".
OL,26,@nD@KOUsD@VO]wD@SOU{D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FThe barrister also said that the
OL,7,Fdifference between being in "the Army"
OL,8,Fand being a member of Sinn Fein was
OL,9,Fnot a "clear either/or choice".
OL,11,FShe added: "The claimants' case is
OL,12,Fthat none of these bombings in the
OL,13,FUnited Kingdom mainland took place
OL,14,Fwithout the knowledge and agreement of
OL,15,Fthe defendant in his role in the
OL,16,FProvisional IRA and latterly as a
OL,17,Fmember of the seven-man Army Council."
OL,26,@oD@]OUoD@fO]qD@GOUqD@^O]sD@LOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/13
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,444,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1773778273
OL,3,CGerry Adams tells High Court he 'never
OL,4,Cheld any role or rank within the IRA'
OL,6,FShe concluded: "There is no doubt that
OL,7,Fthe defendant contributed to the peace
OL,8,Fin Northern Ireland, but the claimants
OL,9,Fsay that on the evidence he also
OL,10,Fcontributed to the war."
OL,12,FMs Studd also told the court that Mr
OL,13,FAdams had "a foot in each camp" of the
OL,14,Fmilitary and political sides of the
OL,15,FIrish Republican movement, and that
OL,16,Fwas likely "as involved as the people
OL,17,Fwho planted and detonated those bombs".
OL,19,FThe trial is due to conclude later in
OL,20,FMarch.
OL,26,@nD@POUrD@XO]uD@KOUuD@_O]xD@LOUyD@fO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/13
